org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.experiment

Class ReplayExperiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.experiment.ReplayExperiment

  • public class ReplayExperiment
extends Object
    The ReplayExperiment loads experimentData from an experiment and "re-runs" it. Doing so, we can use already written experiment observer to analyise experimentData of already run experiments i.e. caculate the average reward per step.
